Subject: Sensitive Data ShareDetails - insert "Last Modified" column
Description: We've reinstalled Netwrix Enterprise Auditor 11.6 on our server and trying to figure out how to add the "Last Modified" column to the Sensitive Date ShareDetails table.
Solution_Comment__c: We added the "Last Modified' column to the "Share details" report by SQL View Creation by Joining the SA_FS_DLPResults_ShareDetails and SA_FS_CleanupView. The report re-publishing resolved the issue with the report
